<div id="I_file">&lt;cstdio&gt;</div>
<h1>L_tmpnam</h1>
<div id="I_description">Minimum length for temporary file name</div>
<section id="description">
This macro constant expands to an integral expression corresponding to the size needed for an array of <tt>char</tt> elements to hold the longest file name string possibly generated by <a href="/tmpnam">tmpnam</a>.<br>
</section>
